Key drivers:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Value driver #1
\series default
: Scalable growth: the faster you grow, the larger you get.
 The larger you get, the more difficult it is to keep growing.
 How good is your firm at scaling up growth?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Value driver #2
\series default
: Sustainable margins: success attracts competition and competition can
 hurt margins.
 How strong is your company's competitive edge?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Value driver #3
\series default
: Quality growth: growth has value, only if accompanied by excess returns.
 Do you see your firm generating returns significantly higher than its cost
 of funding? 
\end_layout

